metadata.name: WonderHome Open Edition 1 #1/1000
metadata.description:
"Wonder Homes" is an Open Edition NFT that captures the essence of fulfilling one's dreams. The artwork portrays a picturesque view of a beautifully designed house amidst a serene surrounding. The vibrant colors and intricate details of the image evoke a sense of wonder and inspiration, reminding us that anything is possible if we dare to dream. The NFT is a celebration of the power of imagination, hard work, and perseverance, serving as a reminder that our dreams can indeed come true if we believe in ourselves and keep striving towards our goals.  
Will be needed for future burns.  
Final burn will grant wallet holders ETH
